### TechTrack AI - REST Client API Tester
### Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client) to use this file
### Click "Send Request" above any request to test it

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### AUTH ROUTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Signup (Register new user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Get current user (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### PROFILE ROUTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 4. Get user profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Update user profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### RESUME ROUTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 6. Generate Resume (AI-powered)
POST {{baseUrl}}/resume/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobTitle": "Software Engineer",
  "skills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"],
  "experience": "3 years of full-stack development"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### INTERVIEW ROUTES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 7. Generate Interview Questions
POST {{baseUrl}}/interview/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobTitle": "Frontend Developer",
  "techStack": ["React", "TypeScript", "CSS"],
  "difficulty": "medium"
}

###

### 8. Get interview history
GET {{baseUrl}}/interview/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
